1. This will be a GREAT and ENJOYABLE project!!!

2. Creating the seed list and database 

5 Models

Workout App:

* user
user has many user_workouts 
user has many workouts thru user_workouts


                
* user_workouts
belongs_to user
belongs_to workout

* workout 
has_many user_workouts
has_many users thru user_workout
has_many yoga
has_many cardio
has_many strength


* yoga 
belongs to workout

* cardio 
belongs_to workout

* strength 
belongs_to workout




migration table:

user: 
t.string email
t.string first_name
t.string last_name
t.integer age

user_workout: 
t.string name 
t.integer user_id
t.integer workouts_id
t.string favorites 


workout:
t.string name 
t.string workout_type 
t.integer yoga_id 
t.integer cardio_id 
t.integer strength_id

yoga: 
t.string name 
t.string instensity 
t.integer duration

cardio: 
t.string name 
t.string instensity 
t.integer duration

strength:
t.string name 
t.string instensity 
t.integer duration


As a user, I want to be able to create a workout (type), save it to the database
as a user, I want to enter my name to retrieve my workouts
